OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPM backs calls for P&O     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FFerries boss Peter         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FHebblethwaite to resign    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The prime minister has backed calls for
OL,6, the boss of P&O Ferries to resign over 
OL,7, the no-notice sackings of 800 staff.   
OL,9,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps called
OL,10,Ffor Peter Hebblethwaite to step down   
OL,11,Fafter his "brazen" law breaking.       
OL,13,FMr Hebblethwaite admitted to MPs that  
OL,14,Fhe broke the law by not consulting     
OL,15,Fworkers but said he would do the same  
OL,16,Fagain if he had to.                    
OL,18,FAsked if Boris Johnson supported Mr    
OL,19,FShapps' call for P&O's boss to quit, a 
OL,20,FNo 10 spokesman said: "Yes."           
